OL,3,CEngland and penalty shootouts: Why is
OL,4,Cthere more confidence than ever?
OL,6,FKnockout football has a habit of
OL,7,Fproducing the ultimate test of nerve:
OL,8,Fthe penalty shootout.
OL,10,FThe opening day of the Round of 32
OL,11,Fserved as an early reminder of that,
OL,12,Fwith Paraguay dramatically eliminating
OL,13,FGermany and Morocco knocking out the
OL,14,FNetherlands.
OL,16,FFor England, penalties have
OL,17,Ftraditionally brought more pain than
OL,18,Fcelebration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
