OL,3,CEngland and penalty shootouts: Why is
OL,4,Cthere more confidence than ever?
OL,6,FThe images of Stuart Pearce and Chris
OL,7,FWaddle missing in the 1990 World Cup
OL,8,Fsemi-final remain among the most
OL,9,Fenduring in English football.
OL,11,FSix years later, Gareth Southgate
OL,12,Fsuffered similar heartbreak when he
OL,13,Fmissed the decisive penalty in the
OL,14,FEuro 96 semi-final at Wembley.
OL,16,FBetween 1996 and 2012, England took
OL,17,Fpart in seven tournament penalty
OL,18,Fshootouts, but won just one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
