OL,3,CEngland and penalty shootouts: Why is
OL,4,Cthere more confidence than ever?
OL,6,FIt was Southgate, as England manager,
OL,7,Fwho helped rewrite that story. At the
OL,8,F2018 World Cup in Russia, England beat
OL,9,FColombia on penalties to secure their
OL,10,Ffirst shootout victory at a major
OL,11,Ftournament for 22 years.
OL,13,FWith Jordan Pickford in goal,
OL,14,FEngland's record from the spot has
OL,15,Fimproved considerably.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
