OL,3,CEngland and penalty shootouts: Why is
OL,4,Cthere more confidence than ever?
OL,6,FHis now-famous water bottle, covered
OL,7,Fwith detailed notes on opposition
OL,8,Fpenalty takers, played its part as
OL,9,FEngland defeated Switzerland on
OL,10,Fpenalties in the quarter-finals of
OL,11,FEuro 2024.
OL,13,FShould England face another shootout,
OL,14,Fthey will also have confidence in the
OL,15,Fquality of their penalty takers.
OL,17,FCaptain Harry Kane has shown different
OL,18,Fapproaches from the spot during his
OL,19,Fcareer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
