OL,3,CEngland and penalty shootouts: Why is
OL,4,Cthere more confidence than ever?
OL,6,FEngland could also turn to Ivan Toney,
OL,7,Fwidely regarded as one of the best
OL,8,Fpenalty takers in world football. His
OL,9,Fdistinctive technique sees him
OL,10,Fmaintain eye contact with the
OL,11,Fgoalkeeper for almost his entire run-
OL,12,Fup, barely looking at the ball before
OL,13,Fstriking it.
OL,15,FPenalty shootouts remain one of
OL,16,Ffootball's cruellest ways to decide a
OL,17,Fmatch.
OL,19,FThe winners celebrate unforgettable
OL,20,Fmoments, but for those who miss, the
OL,21,Fmemories can last a lifetime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
