OL,3,CEngland and penalty shootouts: Why is
OL,4,Cthere more confidence than ever?
OL,6,FFew know that better than Southgate,
OL,7,Fwho has spoken about how he still
OL,8,Fthinks about the penalty he missed at
OL,9,FEuro 96 nearly 30 years ago.
